msgstr "В разделе :guilabel:`Invoicing` в поле :guilabel:`Re-Invoice Expenses` выберите :guilabel:`At cost` или :guilabel:`Sales price`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/expense.rst:0
