msgstr "Затем перетащите примечание в нужное место с помощью значка :icon:`oi-apps` :guilabel:`(шести квадратов)`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/quote_template.rst:154
msgid "To delete any line item from the :guilabel:`Lines` tab (product, section, and/or note), click the :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`(remove record)` icon on the far-right side of the line."
