#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/payment_providers/wire_transfer.rst:5
msgid "The *wire transfer* payment method allows for payment instructions to be shared with a customer after purchasing a product. With a subscription, these payment instructions are shared every time the payment is renewed."
